snippet.title: Fiber Twig (2004, PC) - 01 of 15: Levels 01~04 [1080p60]
snippet.description:
Fiber Twig is Puzzle Lab's 5th Title, and 1st in its "Pipe Mania" series of puzzle games. 

A Pipe Mania-like puzzle game where you link various "twigs" into each other and reach the top

Levels included: 1 (Tutorial) , 2 (Among The Flowers In The Garden Of The Beautiful Enchantress) , 3 (Composing A Seven-Note Melody For The Lady On The Bird) , 4 (Lighting Up The Way For The Star Hunter)
